      "finding": "The entire finding is post-hoc. The authors acknowledge this in Section 6 ('Not a prediction'), but the robustness analyses are structured to retroactively assess a coincidence. Methodologically, the 'look-elsewhere' assessment (Section 5.6) is applied after the match was found, searching through quark species and integer powers. This inflates the apparent specificity. While transparently reported, the post-hoc framework means no statistical inference (even of a non-frequentist kind) is valid.",
